# catalystcenter_wireless_enterprise_ssid (Data Source)

This data source can read the Wireless Enterprise SSID.

## Example Usage

```terraform
data "catalystcenter_wireless_enterprise_ssid" "example" {
  id = "mySSID1"
}
```
